necessary to keep a balance. 
  Gemany is trying to end the negotiations without "excitement 
and panic." This is being done in the closest coordination with 
the Federal Government and Lufthansa, Steinle said. The talks 
with the U.S. company United Airlines on the contentious issue 
of code-sharing, which Lufthansa would like, will be continued 
in Washington on Friday. [passage omitted] 

