<H3> <TI>   Solana: Spain `Will Not Take Part' in Air Strikes </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1402180194 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1700 GMT 
14 Feb 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD1402180194 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] According to Spanish Foreign Minister Javier Solana, 
our country's planes will not take part in the possible attacks 
against Serb positions around Sarajevo. 
  Javier Solana also said that, for the time being, one does 
not consider it necessary to evacuate Spanish citizens residing 
in former Yugoslavia. 

</TEXT>

